&trans  &none      &none  &none     &kp END   &kp HOME   &kp PG_DN    &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans    &none         &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp KP_NUMBER_0  &kp KP_DOT  &kp KP_EQUAL  &kp KP_PLUS      &none
&trans  &kp RSHFT         &trans    &trans    &trans     &trans                                         &kp KP_ENTER  &kp DEL                                                                            &studio_unlock
            >;
