&kp LCTRL  &kp C_MUTE          &kp LWIN  &lt 3 KP_ENTER  &kp SPACE  &mo SCROLL                                                                             &mt RIGHT_SHIFT LANG_ZENKAKUHANKAKU  &kp BSPC                                                                &none
